{
  "id": "69ae9f21142eff98c6b69f79",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:フローチャートこと",
  "created": 1773051702,
  "updated": 1773051703,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ae9f21142eff98c6b69f79",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:フローチャートこと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051702,
      "updated": 1773051702
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f360000000000341564",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051702,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341565",
      "text": "はいはーい、今日のゆるトーク会はじまるよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341566",
      "text": "テーマは「フローチャート」！📊",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341567",
      "text": "なんかさ、授業で出てきたんだけどさ、最初見たとき",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341568",
      "text": "「なにこの四角とひし形のダンジョンマップ」って思ったんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341569",
      "text": "りか、これって要するに「手順の地図」みたいなやつで合ってる？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156c",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156d",
      "text": "フローチャートは、処理の流れを図で表したもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156e",
      "text": "アルゴリズム（問題解決の手順）を可視化するためのツールだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034156f",
      "text": "例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341570",
      "text": " 楕円：開始・終了",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341571",
      "text": " 四角：処理",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341572",
      "text": " ひし形：条件分岐",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341573",
      "text": "といった標準記号で構成される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341574",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341575",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/フローチャート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341576",
      "text": "プログラム設計や業務プロセス設計で広く使われている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341577",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341578",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341579",
      "text": "あー！それそれ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157a",
      "text": "「もしHPが0ならゲームオーバー」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157b",
      "text": "みたいな分岐が、ひし形だったやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157c",
      "text": "つまりゲームのイベントとか、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157d",
      "text": "「こうなったら次これ」って流れを図にした攻略チャートみたいな感じ？🎮",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034157f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341580",
      "text": "いい例えだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341581",
      "text": "RPGのイベント進行は、実質的に状態遷移と分岐の集合。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341582",
      "text": "フローチャートでかなり表現しやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341583",
      "text": "例えば：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341584",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341585",
      "text": " code:flowchart.mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341586",
      "text": "  graph TD",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341587",
      "text": "  A((開始))-->B[敵に遭遇]-->C{戦う？}",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341588",
      "text": "  C -->|はい|D[勝利]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341589",
      "text": "  C -->|いいえ|E[逃げる]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158a",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158c",
      "text": "このような思考整理ができる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034158f",
      "text": "まあ……それは、まるで物語の道筋のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341590",
      "text": "物語にも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341591",
      "text": "「もし彼があの手紙を読まなければ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341592",
      "text": "「もし彼女があの町へ行かなければ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341593",
      "text": "そんな分かれ道がございますでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341594",
      "text": "フローチャートとは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341595",
      "text": "まるで物語の運命を、静かな地図として描いたもののようで……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341596",
      "text": "なんだか詩的でございますね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341597",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341598",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f370000000000341599",
      "text": "おお〜、あやの文学モード出たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159a",
      "text": "でも確かに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159b",
      "text": "人生フローチャートとか作れそうじゃない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159c",
      "text": "「宿題やる？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159d",
      "text": "→ YES：えらい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159e",
      "text": "→ NO：明日泣く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f37000000000034159f",
      "text": "みたいなｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a2",
      "text": "それはかなり現実的なモデルだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a3",
      "text": "フローチャートの強みは三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a4",
      "text": " 1. 処理の全体像が見える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a5",
      "text": " 2. 分岐の漏れを発見できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a6",
      "text": " 3. 他人と共有しやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a7",
      "text": "プログラムを書く前に作ると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a8",
      "text": "バグ（設計ミス）を減らせる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415aa",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ab",
      "text": "なるほど……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ac",
      "text": "文章で長く説明されるよりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ad",
      "text": "図として眺める方が、心にすっと入ることもございますわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ae",
      "text": "読書でも、ときどき",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415af",
      "text": "人物関係図があると助かりますもの。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b2",
      "text": "あー！わかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b3",
      "text": "推理小説とか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b4",
      "text": "登場人物多すぎ問題あるよねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b5",
      "text": "それもある意味フローチャートの親戚かも？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b8",
      "text": "正確には少し違うが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415b9",
      "text": "情報を図式化するという意味では近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ba",
      "text": "フローチャートは特に",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415bb",
      "text": "[**** 時間の流れ（プロセス）]を表す点が特徴。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415bd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415be",
      "text": "なるほどなるほど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415bf",
      "text": "じゃあまとめると〜",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c0",
      "text": "フローチャートって",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c1",
      "text": " 手順を図にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c2",
      "text": " 分岐が見える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c3",
      "text": " ゲームのイベントとかプログラムに便利",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c4",
      "text": "って感じだね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c7",
      "text": "ええ、とても分かりやすいまとめですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c8",
      "text": "まるで迷路を上から見渡すように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415c9",
      "text": "物事の流れを眺められる――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ca",
      "text": "それがフローチャートの魅力なのかもしれませんね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415cc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415cd",
      "text": "同意する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415ce",
      "text": "複雑な世界を整理するための、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415cf",
      "text": "[** 思考の地図]。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d0",
      "text": "それがフローチャートだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d3",
      "text": "よし！今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d4",
      "text": "フローチャート＝",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d5",
      "text": "「[** 考えごとの攻略マップ]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d6",
      "text": "ってことで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d7",
      "text": "じゃ、次回のゆるトークもよろしく〜！🎮",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae9f3700000000003415d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773051703,
      "updated": 1773051703
    }
  ]
}